# ── Per-case LLM explanations (regenerated each cleanroom) ────────────────
# 122 .txt files reproduced verbatim by `tools/full_cleanroom_v2.sh`.
# Tracking them would create churn on every run; the canonical snapshot is
# instead under `evaluation/results/runs/<timestamp>/` and the per-run JSON
# `pipeline_report.json` carries decision metadata for every case.
Note_AIFA/evaluation/results/pipeline_explanations/

